Two lime wedges are placed on the plate next to the salad. The tofu is drizzled with a sauce and presented on a skewer. The dish is plated on a white plate, and chopsticks are placed on top of the salad.

The image shows two glasses filled with a layered vegan parfait. The ingredients include chia seed pudding, raspberries, mango, granola, and a dark berry jelly. The post is tagged with #glutenfree and #plantsheal, indicating a focus on healthy and plant-based eating.
The image shows a plated vegan dish consisting of rice and pea protein kabobs on cinnamon sticks, served with asparagus and a decorative sauce.

The image shows a plate of vegan spaghetti. The spaghetti is made from light, thin, gluten-free brown rice. It's served with roasted tomatoes, steamed asparagus, and a green sauce made from Trader Joe's Vegan Kale, Cashew & Basil Pesto.

The image shows a vegan cashew-coconut cheesecake topped with berry sauce and fresh raspberries, garnished with mint leaves. There is also a strawberry on the plate, and white flowers in the background.

The image shows a plate of tofu scramble with colorful vegetables and edible flowers, alongside a glass of a creamy-colored beverage. The post is by vegan_genie, suggesting a focus on vegan food and healthy lifestyle.
